# [EN] Non-sensitive Runtime settings live in packages/config/src/index.ts.
# [CN] Runtime 非敏感配置维护在 packages/config/src/index.ts。
# [EN] This file contains only the deployment secret required for analytics delivery.
# [CN] 本文件只保留统计事件投递所需的部署密钥。
# [EN] Use a random secret of at least 32 characters. It must exactly match the WebUI
# [CN] 使用至少 32 字符的随机密钥，并确保它与 WebUI 的
# [EN] ANALYTICS_INGEST_SECRET and must be different from auth or database credentials.
# [CN] ANALYTICS_INGEST_SECRET 完全一致，且不得复用认证或数据库凭据。
ANALYTICS_WRITE_KEY="replace-with-a-32-byte-random-secret"
